http://tldp.org/LDP/lpg/node11.html
http://www.tutorialspoint.com/unix_system_calls/waitpid.htm
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/12444679/poll-function-in-c-how-does-it-work
https://www.gnu.org/software/libc/manual/html_node/Creating-a-Pipe.html#Creating-a-Pipe


Testing methodology
======

Most of the testing in this project was done by a combination of observing the 
output of the program in certain inputs, reading the printed messages from the 
program, and using the gdb debugger along with breakpoints to view the state 
of the program at certain points.

